data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home that has been beautifully updated with modern features while still retaining its classic appeal. The house boasts a walk-out basement and a spacious 2-car garage, providing ample space for all your needs. To top it off, the property sits on a generous half-acre lot in a prime location that is sure to capture your heart.
